  "text": "SAXS measurements were conducted at BioCAT (ID18; Advanced Photon Source, Argonne National Laboratory) as described previously by [CITATION_1] and [CITATION_2] . RNA solutions (0.4 mg/ml in 20 mM Tris-HCl) with 0-10 mM MgCl 2 were equilibrated at 37 C before each measurement (four 2 s exposures), over Q = 0.008-0.2 Å À1 ( Figure S1A ).",
